description: The Deka MSCI EUR Corporates Climate Change ESG UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the MSCI EUR Corporates IG Climate Change ESG Select Index (price index). Sustainability criteria are taken into account in the composition of the index universe. The constituents are selected based on their CO2 emissions profile.
name: Deka MSCI EUR Corporates Climate Change ESG UCITS ETF
